Lumbar pseudo-tail associated with dermal sinus - A case report.

Seromenho-Santos A(1), Valsassina R(2), Pimentel J(3), Miguéns J(4), Faria 
CC(5).

Author information:
(1)Department of Neurosurgery, Centro Hospitalar de Lisboa Ocidental, Hospital 
de Egas Moniz, Lisboa, Portugal; Department to Anatomy, Faculdade de Medicina, 
Universidade de Lisboa, Lisboa, Portugal. Electronic address: 
alexandrasantos@campus.ul.pt.
(2)Departmet of Pediatrics, Hospital Beatriz Ângelo, Loures, Portugal.
(3)Neuropathology Laboratory, Department of Neurology, Hospital de Santa Maria, 
